101
00:13:39,040 --> 00:13:41,000
Veľmi krvácaš!

102
00:13:42,390 --> 00:13:46,730
Teraz sa nestaraj o mňa. Šťastie, že sme prežili.
Ak nás však chytia,

103
00:13:46,730 --> 00:13:48,810
